Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000002583FC292D0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' leading to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call' across cases where both activities occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' in the event log timeline
Latest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' in the event log timeline
Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Comparison of average duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Comparison of total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' against 'Accepted + In Progress' in the most frequent process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' leading to a change in 'impact' level
Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' without leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when `ACTIVITY` != 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with 'High' impact versus 'Medium' or 'Low' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case grouped by the last value of impact filtered by the function ma == 'High' where ma is the last value of impact

Name: Time until first occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time from 'Accepted + Wait' to the next occurrence of any 'Completed +' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed +'
